    {
      "id": "t_note",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 675,
      "width": 1040,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "⚠️ The Critical Rule:\n\nServices find each other via GetComponentInChildren — this works in Awake, so execution order doesn't matter.\n\nNEVER call another service's methods in your own Awake() or Start().\nInstead, let each service self-initialize and call them later (in Update, or via UnityEvents).\n\nIf Service A needs Service B to be ready, use async initialization with await.\nThe NPCSceneInitializationController orchestrates this with ordered phases.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#fbbf24",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "note_box",
      "originalText": "⚠️ The Critical Rule:\n\nServices find each other via GetComponentInChildren — this works in Awake, so execution order doesn't matter.\n\nNEVER call another service's methods in your own Awake() or Start().\nInstead, let each service self-initialize and call them later (in Update, or via UnityEvents).\n\nIf Service A needs Service B to be ready, use async initialization with await.\nThe NPCSceneInitializationController orchestrates this with ordered phases.",
      "autoResize": true
    },
